Hi Leandra, I'm sorry to hear that you're having trouble downloading a transaction. Could you please let me know which platform or service you are using? This will help me provide more specific instructions.

Thanks for letting me know, Leandra. To download a transaction in Newsbreak Ad Manager, you can follow these steps:
1. Log in to your Newsbreak Ad Manager account.
2. Navigate to the 'Billing' section from the main menu.
3. Find the transaction you want to download and click on it.
4. Look for a 'Download' or 'Export' option, usually available as a button or link.
If you still don't see an option to download the transaction, please let me know and I can assist further.
There is no download or export option

I've sent an email to our support team to look into this issue for you, Leandra. They should get back to you soon. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to let me know!
You're welcome, Leandra! If you need any more help, just let me know. Have a great day!
